member.name: HTTP_SERVICE_CONFIG_URLACL_PARAM
member.summary: TheHTTP_SERVICE_CONFIG_URLACL_PARAM structure is used to specify the permissions associated with a particular record in the URL namespace reservation store. It is a member of the structure.

member.name: HTTP_SERVICE_CONFIG_URLACL_PARAM.pStringSecurityDescriptor
member.summary: A pointer to aSecurity Descriptor Definition Language (SDDL) string that contains the permissions associated with this URL namespace reservation record.
